cs.SY, cs.Optimization, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.CE 

The paper deals with optimal control problems, which are typically studied in the control systems (cs.SY) and optimization (cs.Optimization) sub-categories. The use of sparsity-promoting penalties is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.NA), which suggests that these sub-categories are also likely. Finally, the paper includes a numerical example involving a partial differential equation, which is a common topic in computational engineering (cs.CE).
